04:48.830 --> 04:51.332
being my sweet, charming self.

04:51.416 --> 04:52.417
And that worked?

04:52.500 --> 04:54.252
Well, proof is in the pudding, right?

04:54.335 --> 04:55.670
I don't like pudding.

04:55.753 --> 04:57.422
Well, forget the pudding.

04:57.505 --> 04:59.799
The point is,
is you're young, Sam, you know.

04:59.882 --> 05:02.093
