06:36.604 --> 06:40.608
I was just having fun

06:40.691 --> 06:43.152
with a group of strangers

06:43.236 --> 06:46.906
who had nothing to do with autism.

06:46.989 --> 06:48.825
And, again, I love you guys.

06:48.908 --> 06:51.786
But this guy, this bartender I met,

06:51.869 --> 06:53.204
he is so...

06:53.704 --> 06:55.498
his life is so crazy!

06:55.581 --> 07:01.879
And risk-taking and ordinary, you know?

07:01.963 --> 07:06.717
And I just...
I realized that that's, um...

07:08.553 --> 07:10.638
It's just a life Sam's never gonna have.

07:14.183 --> 07:15.560
So, um...

07:18.104 --> 07:20.064
I don't know. I just...

07:21.524 --> 07:23.526
[sighs deeply]

07:25.528 --> 07:28.156
I made lemon squares, um...

07:28.239 --> 07:30.575
so don't anybody be shy.

07:31.367 --> 07:33.119
They're overzested.

07:33.911 --> 07:35.913
[applause]

07:37.874 --> 07:41.461
Your dad's right, bro. A girl is fair game
until there's a ring on it.

07:41.544 --> 07:42.378
A wedding ring.

07:42.462 --> 07:45.298
An engagement ring means she's ready
for one more mistake.

07:47.383 --> 07:49.093
Okay, this is perfect.

07:51.429 --> 07:52.555
Watch this.

07:55.141 --> 07:57.643
[Sam]  Sometimes I wish I was smooth,
like Zahid.

07:59.020 --> 08:02.064
Of all the people I know,
he's the best at girls.

08:26.255 --> 08:27.465
And that's how you do it.

08:28.049 --> 08:29.509
Now I'm gonna hide in the back,

08:29.592 --> 08:33.471
