09:46.127 --> 09:47.837
-What's wrong with it?
-Nothing.

09:47.920 --> 09:50.423
I don't understand
why you do all that working out

09:50.506 --> 09:52.842
if you're not gonna flaunt
your cute figure.

09:52.925 --> 09:55.303
[scoffs] Oh, my God.
You want me to dress sluttier?

09:55.386 --> 09:56.637
Why are you canceling it?

09:56.721 --> 09:57.805
Identity theft.

09:57.888 --> 10:01.434
Sweetie, it was a compliment.
You're adorable under all that bulk.

10:01.517 --> 10:02.977
