11:05.831 --> 11:08.125
Do you know the one thing
that brings me joy?

11:08.209 --> 11:10.086
Other than the failures of my brother?

11:12.088 --> 11:15.007
It is girls with actual talent.

11:15.549 --> 11:17.093
-Like you!
-Mm-hmm.

11:18.469 --> 11:20.888
